data.description: Beautiful Lennar home, 2,909 sq ft, 5 bedrooms, 3 baths.  Views of the Rincon Mountains, common area behind large enclosed backyard, & good size side yards for gardens/dog runs etc. This home has all of the ''bells and whistles'' including open floorplan, 2 dining areas, breakfast bar, stainless appliances & granite countertops, large bedrooms, walk in closets and air conditioned 3 car garage. Lower room could be another bedroom suite, game room or den with 2 closets & double door entry. Convenient to I-10, schools, rec center & park.
